WEBVTT

00:02.449 --> 00:04.586
- [SCREAMS]
- ANDY: You think I'm a monster

00:04.589 --> 00:05.683
for trying to kill him?

00:05.686 --> 00:06.785
You think you're better than me.

00:06.787 --> 00:08.186
I'm just doing what has to be done.

00:09.689 --> 00:11.891
You've been sharing
dreams with Andy for months

00:11.894 --> 00:13.334
and now you're afraid to sleep.

00:13.337 --> 00:16.360
It's like he's probing my mind,
searching for my weaknesses.

00:16.363 --> 00:18.363
I'm never joining the Inner Circle.

00:18.365 --> 00:21.311
ANDY: Something's changed.
I can't feel her anymore.

00:21.314 --> 00:23.835
People need help. I can't just
sit here and watch them suffer.

00:23.837 --> 00:26.471
I know it's dangerous, but I
can't use the serum as a crutch.

00:26.473 --> 00:29.374
All we asked for was your
loyalty, and you betrayed us.

00:29.377 --> 00:31.343
Reeva, I didn't do this.

00:31.345 --> 00:32.511
[SINGING HIGH TONE]

00:32.512 --> 00:34.546
[GROANING, SCREAMING]

00:36.116 --> 00:37.983
I have a job for your Purifiers.

00:37.985 --> 00:41.286
This is an essential part
of the plan. Get it done.

00:41.288 --> 00:43.121
The Purifiers are hitting the Morlocks.

00:43.123 --> 00:44.690
Clarice needs our help evacuating.

00:44.692 --> 00:46.817
Over here, let's go! Let's go, let's go!

00:46.820 --> 00:48.393
- I'm not leaving without Clarice!
- Caitlin,

00:48.395 --> 00:49.694
take John's car, he's staying.

00:51.275 --> 00:52.997
CAITLIN: Lauren, try to use your powers.

00:53.000 --> 00:54.232
I can't reach them.

00:54.234 --> 00:57.536
Get out of the way!

00:57.538 --> 00:58.570
Clarice, come on.

01:00.674 --> 01:02.841
No!

01:04.000 --> 01:10.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:12.252 --> 01:14.553
THUNDERBIRD: Okay, what's wrong?

01:14.555 --> 01:16.655
Nothing.

01:16.657 --> 01:18.523
Clarice, come on.

01:18.525 --> 01:20.392
It's just...

01:20.394 --> 01:22.561
my whole life, I've been running...

01:22.563 --> 01:25.997
From myself, from everything, really.

01:25.999 --> 01:28.266
And now I'm here with
you, and I just feel...

01:30.337 --> 01:33.338
I don't know, I just feel...

01:33.340 --> 01:36.174
Happy.

01:36.176 --> 01:38.176
- [CHUCKLES SOFTLY]
- Yeah.

01:39.847 --> 01:42.681
But sometimes I feel like
I don't deserve to be.

01:44.118 --> 01:46.551
Why wouldn't you deserve to be happy?

01:46.553 --> 01:49.020
I've made a lot of really
bad decisions in my life.

01:51.892 --> 01:53.725
Never mind.

01:53.727 --> 01:56.228
I don't want to talk about it.

01:56.230 --> 01:58.630
No.

01:58.632 --> 02:02.134
No, come on. Tell me.

02:04.204 --> 02:07.806
Well, you know, years ago, when
I got mixed up with the, um,

02:07.808 --> 02:09.274
with the Brotherhood...

02:09.276 --> 02:11.810
you know, I really hated myself.

02:11.812 --> 02:13.812
God, I felt so trapped.

02:15.315 --> 02:17.949
I would lie there at night

02:17.951 --> 02:21.386
and open a portal to the stars

02:21.388 --> 02:25.290
and just wish that I was... somewhere,

02:25.292 --> 02:27.425
anywhere else.

02:27.427 --> 02:28.660
Show me.

02:30.464 --> 02:33.098
Okay.

02:35.302 --> 02:37.135
[THUNDERBIRD CHUCKLES SOFTLY]

02:37.137 --> 02:39.747
You know, when things got
really bad, I used to think about

02:39.750 --> 02:42.474
portaling to nowhere, and just going.

02:42.476 --> 02:45.110
Being everywhere.

02:45.112 --> 02:47.746
In the spaces between everything.

02:53.453 --> 02:56.421
Clarice, believe me,

02:56.423 --> 02:59.119
nobody in the Underground is perfect.

02:59.122 --> 03:02.093
I mean, most of us came here
because we needed redemption.

03:02.095 --> 03:04.280
That's why, even now,

03:04.283 --> 03:07.365
I think there is still
hope for Lorna, and Andy.

03:08.969 --> 03:10.669
For all of us.

03:12.339 --> 03:14.339
Are you saying that I should stay here?

03:15.843 --> 03:17.542
With the rest of the broken toys?

03:22.049 --> 03:24.482
Always.

