what happened in the tunnels.

37:43.477 --> 37:44.743
What about it?

37:44.745 --> 37:47.230
I went down there. I did
exactly what you said to do.

37:47.233 --> 37:49.919
And what I saw didn't
look like a terrorist camp.

37:50.916 --> 37:52.784
There were children down
there, there were families,

37:52.786 --> 37:54.753
